*********Onboarding - new hire, contrator
    1. Good background check
    2. Standard operating procedures
    3.  Non-disclosure agreement (NDA)
    4. Specialized issues
    5. Rules of behavior
    6. General rule of policy

*********Offboarding -
    1.disable account
    2.Return credential
    3.exit interview
    4.knowledge transfer


*********(PII) Personal Identifiable information



